DL LAB ASSIGNMENT 9

Main concept used
LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory)

LSTM is a special type of RNN (Recurrent Neural Network).

Used for:

stock prediction
weather prediction
speech recognition
text generation
sequence learning
Why LSTM?

Normal neural networks do not remember previous values.

Stock prices depend on past prices.

LSTM can remember previous time steps.

Your dataset

The file Stock_prices.csv contains historical stock values.

You are using:

Close price

Only closing price is used for prediction.

Code explanation
